<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />，<delay20 />
你每天都能按时早起，<delay8 />真厉害！<pageBreak /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你是有什么<delay8 />秘诀吗？</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦！<delay20 />你过奖了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像我这样很普通啦！<delay frames="30" />
不过我确实有提醒自己<delay8 />每天早点睡觉<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你口中的“普通”，于我可是一大难题啊！<delay frames="30" />
我最不擅长根据计划按部就班地做事情了～<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就没有什么<delay20 />轻松的、<delay8 />
容易做到的方法吗？</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 03 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯～<delay20 />我想想<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="8" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay8 />
<20_3 arg="6" />你有什么好主意吗？</message>
	<message label="004_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">早点睡</message>
	<message label="004_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">早起做些自己喜欢的事情</message>
	<message label="004_c" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">干脆别睡</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />有道理！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要想早起，还是得要早睡才行呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />诶！<delay frames="30" />
只有这一个办法吗？<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你们两个<delay20 />真自律啊～<delay frames="30" />
<20_2 arg="7" />这也是你俩的<delay8 />
一大优点啊！</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没关系的，<20_2 arg="4" /><delay8 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />！<delay20 />
<20_3 arg="5" /><delay20 /><anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在你能够做到早睡早起之前，<delay20 />
我会负起责任<delay8 />助你一臂之力的！</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这就<delay20 />不麻烦你了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay20 />这主意挺不错的呢！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果早上有定好计划的话，<delay20 />
无论多早应该都能爬起来！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯，<delay8 />我想想<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<20_2 arg="7" />早起读书，<delay20 /><20_2 arg="3" />或者做点运动，
你看怎么样？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还有这招啊！<10_4 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说起来，<delay20 />我确实有
买来还没来得及读的书呢～<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><delay20 />一想起来就忍不住想读了！<delay frames="30" /><20_2 arg="8" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯！<delay20 />那就去读那本书吧！</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><20_2 arg="7" />你可不要太过着迷，<delay20 />
结果反而变成熬夜看书哦。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呃<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="3" />，
没想到你还挺风趣的呢，<delay frames="30" />
竟然会开这种玩笑<20_3 arg="6" /><tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对啊！<20_2 arg="3" /><delay20 />只要不睡就行了啊！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你可真是个天才！<pageBreak /><20_2 arg="7" />这个方法我应该可以做到！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我今晚回去<delay8 />就试试！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你、<delay20 />你别当真了呀！<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这里不愧是<delay8 />曾经的无人岛啊！<delay20 />
野生的植物特别多！</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是呀！<delay frames="30" />
在这里可以看到各种花朵争奇斗艳，<delay20 />
我真的<delay8 />很开心！</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />同感～！<delay frames="40" />
这里还有好多我没有养过的花，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看得我心痒痒啊！</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />，<delay20 />
你真的很喜欢花呢！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也喜欢<delay8 />用花来装饰房间哦。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在家里装饰一些花朵，<delay8 />能让家里看着更明亮！<10_4 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而在这座岛上<delay8 />看到的花，<delay20 />
让人觉得它们最自然的状态也很棒！</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我懂你的意思！<10_4 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太阳光<delay8 />照射在花朵上的光景实在太美了，<delay20 />
我可以看上一整天。<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，如果一直待在户外看花，<delay20 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总是会受到虫子的搅扰呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果是很怕虫的人，<delay20 />
应该很难在这座岛上生活吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />不过，<delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在你适应这里虫子多的环境前，<delay8 />
我会帮你的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有什么事就跟我说！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />谢谢你！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />，<delay8 />
总觉得你好帅气呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />就是这样，<delay20 />
我的那个小弟<tag a="110" b="0" />不对！<delay20 /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是我的朋友！<delay20 />
被我成功解救了！</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Clapping" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇，<delay8 />太厉害了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这种事情我实在学不来！<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />，<delay20 />
我有点羡慕你那种坚强勇敢的精神呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了，<delay20 />
我可以模仿一下你说话的方式吗？</message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />诶？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我怕<delay20 />那不适合你，
还是别学我了吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那<delay20 />只模仿“<tag a="110" b="5" />”这个口头禅也可以，
请让我用用吧！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Apologize" target="actor" targetSpec="" />拜托你了！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只是口头禅的话，<delay20 />你要学就学吧<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="206" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的吗？！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太好了～！<delay frames="30" />
谢谢你！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="207" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然我觉得你还是<delay8 />
保持原样比较好<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>